<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.3.4">
<l>māytta leṇṇi vāymulai tanta māyap pēyuyir</l>
<l>māytta vāya māyaṉē vāma ṉaṉē mātavā</l>
<l>pūttaṇ mālai koṇṭuṉṉaip pōtāl vaṇaṅkē ṉēluniṉ</l>
<l>pūttaṇ mālai neṭumuṭikkup puṉaiyuṅ kaṇṇi yeṉatuyirē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O Dark one from the cowherders who put an end to the life of the deceptive demoness</l>
<l>who gave [her] breast to [your] mouth, counting on putting an end [to you], Vāmana, Mādava,</l>
<l>even though I don’t bow to you through [all] the time with a cool garland of flowers,</l>
<l>my life-breath is a chaplet that decorated your tall crown with a cool flower garland.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
